reviewText: I love these stories, I love these movies, I love the English dubbed versions, and I love this whole series. Thank Mr. Baryshnikov!

The stories on these videos/DVDs are classic.  The animation is simple but very artistic.  It is the audio that is really amazing- excellent music and voices, articulation- very outstanding.

I have 3 children between the ages of 3 and 9, and all 3 of them were captivated by these timeless stories and the beautiful voices and music.
